Effective Date: [Insert Date]

This Privacy Policy explains how GoGigGo ("we," "us," or "our") collects, uses, shares, and protects your information when you use our platform. By using GoGigGo, you agree to the terms of this policy.

Information We Collect:

Account Information: Name, email, phone number, and password.

HVAC Data: Equipment details, service logs, and job notes.

Location Information: Addresses for service locations.

Device Data: IP address, browser type, and platform usage details.

How We Use Your Information:

To provide HVAC job management and location-based services.

To improve our platform and user experience.

To communicate with you about updates or inquiries.

To comply with legal requirements and protect user safety.

Sharing Your Information:

We do not sell your data.

We may share data with service providers to improve functionality.

Legal authorities may access data if required by law.

Your Privacy Choices:

Location Tracking: Disable location sharing in device settings (may limit features).

Account Updates: Change or delete your account information in the app.

Notifications: Opt-out of non-essential communications through settings.

Data Retention:

Data is kept as long as needed for services or legal requirements. You can request deletion by contacting us.

Security:

We use standard methods to protect your data but cannot guarantee complete security.

